name: (Now in App Lab) I Expect You To Die: Home Sweet Home
summary:
Agents, there's been a mission update! This experimental mini-mission has been moved to the App Lab, which you can now complete here: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/5770033666448508/

Become a secret agent in your own living room in this short mixed reality mini-mission. Solve puzzles, escape sinister traps, and use the latest spy technology to defeat Dr. Zor’s evil plans. If the poisonous gas doesn’t get you, then the Zornets definitely will. Stay sharp because HQ expects you to die!
